    @MediaClass(uuid1=218169601,
            uuid2=257,
            uuid3=11776,
            uuid4={6,14,43,52,2,6,1,1},
            definedName="TapeDescriptor",
            description="The TapeDescriptor class describes audio tape or video tape media.",
            symbol="TapeDescriptor")
public class TapeDescriptorImpl
extends EssenceDescriptorImpl
implements TapeDescriptor, TapeDescriptor, Serializable, Cloneable

    Implements the description of audio tape or video tape media. A source package described by a tape descriptor is known as a tape source package.
